sub_title: Thematic expert in developing trainings and workshops
summary: After specializing in environmental science and environmental economics at universities in Wageningen and Tashkent, I gathered nearly 4 years of experience developing and monitoring environmental program on international industrial site in Uzbekistan. I returned to the Netherlands for personal development as a junior researcher. Now I am looking for my next challenge and a place to realize my drive to keep contributing a healthier, cleaner and safer environment.
